    • testConstructor

      @Test @DisplayName("Library constructor") public void testConstructor()

      Verifies that the Library constructor instantiates a library

      Assertions:

      • Instantiates a Library object with an empty members collection
      • Instantiates a >Library object with an empty books collection
      • Instantiates a Library object with an empty loans collection
      • ID numbers should start at 1
      • The duration of a loan should be 21 days
